		<section class="introduce">
			<div class="container text-center md:text-start">
				<h2 class="text-5xl mb-4">Introduction</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 text-xl">
					<section class="flex flex-col gap-8">
						<p>Hi, My name is Techit Thawiang. An <span style="text-decoration:underline;">almost fifteen</span> years old kid with a passion on many thing, especially coding. You can call me Sumo, that's my nickname.</p>
						<p>I'm living in Chonburi, Thailand.<br/>Currently not finding a job or collaboration.</p>
					</section>
					<section class="hidden md:flex flex-col justify-end items-end ">
						<a class="btn" href="/about">
							About Me
							<i class="ph ph-caret-right text-xl"></i>
						</a>
					</section>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
